com.yandex.money.api.model

Class Scope

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.yandex.money.api.model.Scope
  • Direct Known Subclasses:
    Scope.LimitedScope, Scope.MoneySourceScope

    public class Scope
extends java.lang.Object
    Access token's scope. Provides simple and customizable scopes for every occasion. Complete list of scopes is implemented as const fields or creator methods.

    List of scopes:

  • account-info - ACCOUNT_INFO;
  • incoming-transfers - INCOMING_TRANSFERS;
  • money-source - createMoneySourceScope();
  • operation-details - OPERATION_DETAILS;
  • operation-history - OPERATION_HISTORY;
  • payment - createPaymentScopeToPattern(String) or createPaymentScopeToAccount(String);
  • payment-p2p - PAYMENT_P2P or createPaymentP2pLimitedScope();
  • payment-shop - PAYMENT_SHOP or createPaymentShopLimitedScope().
